To download a DataPack of this example for OmniStudio, click here.

The parent and child Integration Procedures transform a list of paired values into a list of keys and values.

{
  "InputList": [
    {
      "Key": "serial_number",
      "Value": "ABC1234"
    },
    {
      "Key": "install_date",
      "Value": "20200101"
    }
  ]
}

To this output:

{
  "OutputList": [
    {
      "serial_number": "ABC1234"
    },
    {
      "install_date": "20200101"
    }
  ]
}

Create the Child Integration Procedure.
